    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = 0.74
    v0 = ((0.44 - tmp) - v1)
    v0 = 0.94
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.abs((v1 + 0.23 + v2 + 0.91)))
    v2 = (wp.sin(wp.abs(v1 + 0.29)) / (wp.cos(v0 + 0.20) * wp.cos(v2 + 0.02)))
    v2 = ((0.84 - wp.exp(v2 + 0.68)) * (0.69 * wp.sin(tmp + 0.47)))
